rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1%就一定唔會發生既?<br />\n都係果句 你咁多主觀前設既仲邊有得討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你開賭場就發喇 賭果個永遠一定輸 嬴左錢唔俾人走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n起完底終於知點解你講既野冇乜營養<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇物流行業嘅巴絲諗緊轉行/已經轉左行？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/328335\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/328335</a>"},{"pid":"22461dcc519f3ad81f7344d4e9665c9359ceb58f","tid":2279961,"uid":57554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef223540090a3c8c5f216a21bdad77c2ffac1f5d","tid":2279961,"uid":86283,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"288eb5b9e8aa5c146364428e5558814094f10a2a","tid":2279961,"uid":57554,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ddbfb9fdd6c3303e31cc3e23921693cef6186d94","tid":2279961,"uid":86283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T08:35:55.000Z","msg":"你唔識就算數啦<br />\n100個賭仔得1個贏你又係點計出黎?<br />\n嬴完又一定要賭返? 賭返又一定輸返?<br />\n你咁多主觀前設既仲邊有得討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T08:42:04.000Z","msg":"哦，咁簡單問一句<br />\n你發左達未？何生輸身家未？馬會死得未？<br />\n<br />\n另外多謝你地啲賭仔貢獻比書簿津貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你係咪覺得自己係天選之人，一定會贏到開巷<br />\n只係時機未到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他人都只係廢柴，佢地全部都唔識<br />\n係得你先可以係賭場上發到達<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n概率同數學係你身上唔適用咁？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T09:20:34.000Z","msg":"嬴錢就一定係嬴到發達唔使做?<br />\n嬴餐飯就唔算嬴既?<br />\n概率數學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1%就一定唔會發生既?<br />\n都係果句 你咁多主觀前設既仲邊有得討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj